<body>
<cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0060a" xml:id="I01.0023.0060a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0060a00" type="honorific"/><cb:docNumber>No. 23</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0060a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>孫遼浮圖銘</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0060a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0060a0101">大魏正光五年歲次甲辰七月己酉朔廿
<lb ed="I" n="0060a02" type="honorific"/>五日癸酉。故蘭倉令孫府君浮圖之銘記。
<lb ed="I" n="0060a03" type="honorific"/>君姓孫。名遼。<note n="0060001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30070"/>＝定【史】</note><note n="0060001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30070"/>【佛拓】，定【史】</note><app n="0060001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">定</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30070"/></rdg></app>州人也。綿緒太原。分流樂
<lb ed="I" n="0060a04" type="honorific"/>安。爵土有因。遂居鉅鹿<note n="0060002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30485"/>＝焉【史】</note><note n="0060002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30485"/>【佛拓】，焉【史】</note><app n="0060002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">焉</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30485"/></rdg></app>。君稟業沖明。惠
<lb ed="I" n="0060a05" type="honorific"/>性天<note n="0060003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">聡＝聰【史】</note><note n="0060003" resp="ihp" type="mod">聡【佛拓】，聰【史】</note><app n="0060003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">聰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">聡</rdg></app>。少懷淨行。長而彌潔。悟三有之无
<lb ed="I" n="0060a06" type="honorific"/>常。體四趣之沈溺。洞達苦空。超鑒十相。是
<lb ed="I" n="0060a07" type="honorific"/>以童丱之年。信心三寶。厥齡十八。禁酒斷
<lb ed="I" n="0060a08" type="honorific"/><note n="0060004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB18861"/>＝肉【史】</note><note n="0060004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB18861"/>【佛拓】，肉【史】</note><app n="0060004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">肉</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB18861"/></rdg></app>。脩齋持戒。心無染縛。善能開化。方便導
<lb ed="I" n="0060a09" type="honorific"/>物。聞其善者。欣若己身。見其<note n="0060005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB08891"/>＝惡【史】</note><note n="0060005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB08891"/>【佛拓】，惡【史】</note><app n="0060005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">惡</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB08891"/></rdg></app>者。引出火
<lb ed="I" n="0060a10" type="honorific"/>宅。又不以支節之痛。亦其无我之念。遂燒
<lb ed="I" n="0060a11" type="honorific"/>兩指。盡身供養。至<note n="0060006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">扵＝於【史】</note><note n="0060006" resp="ihp" type="mod">扵【佛拓】，於【史】</note><app n="0060006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】">扵</rdg></app>經行業道之處。必捨
<lb ed="I" n="0060a12" type="honorific"/>離親愛。敦崇在內。託心禪<app type="star" corresp="#0060001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">定</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30070"/></rdg></app>。永樂道場。至
<lb ed="I" n="0060a13" type="honorific"/>延昌年中。屬　皇上宣帝。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">褒</unclear>蕳<note n="0060007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30493"/>＝舊【史】</note><note n="0060007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30493"/>【佛拓】，舊【史】</note><app n="0060007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">舊</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30493"/></rdg></app>臣。即拜
<lb ed="I" n="0060a14" type="honorific"/>前縣。辭不獲免。俯仰從任。善<app type="star" corresp="#0060006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】">扵</rdg></app>治方。敷揚
<lb ed="I" n="0060a15" type="honorific"/>恩澤。化均魯恭。德侔西門。名振關左。限過
<lb ed="I" n="0060a16" type="honorific"/>將代。百姓愛仰。率土戀慕。若失慈父。還京
<lb ed="I" n="0060a17" type="honorific"/>數年。仍懃道業。將登顯位。以　彰庸績。春
<lb ed="I" n="0060a18" type="honorific"/>秋六十七。前件年日。寢疾三朝。<note n="0060008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">卆＝卒【史】</note><note n="0060008" resp="ihp" type="mod">卆【佛拓】，卒【史】</note><app n="0060008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">卒</lem><rdg wit="【原】">卆</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0060006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】">扵</rdg></app>京師。
<lb ed="I" n="0060a19" type="honorific"/><note n="0060009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30488"/>＝權【史】</note><note n="0060009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30488"/>【佛拓】，權【史】</note><app n="0060009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">權</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30488"/></rdg></app>殯此處。有子顯就。靈鳳。子沖等。追述亡
<lb ed="I" n="0060a20" type="honorific"/>考。精誠之功。敬造浮圖一<note n="0060010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">塸＝區【史】</note><note n="0060010" resp="ihp" type="mod">塸【佛拓】，區【史】</note><app n="0060010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">區</lem><rdg wit="【原】">塸</rdg></app>。置<app type="star" corresp="#0060006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】">扵</rdg></app>　墓所。
<lb ed="I" n="0060a21" type="honorific"/>願令事与須彌等壽。理与日月齊明。永流
<lb ed="I" n="0060a22" type="honorific"/>懿迹。式傳不朽。迺作銘曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0060a23" type="honorific"/>二儀無像。四天傳則。靈<note n="0060011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB09400"/>＝剎【史】</note><note n="0060011" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB09400"/>【佛拓】，剎【史】</note><app n="0060011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剎</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB09400"/></rdg></app>開神。梵堂<note n="0060012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">啔＝啓【史】</note><note n="0060012" resp="ihp" type="mod">啔【佛拓】，啓【史】</note><app n="0060012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">啓</lem><rdg wit="【原】">啔</rdg></app><note n="0060013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30489"/>＝或【史】</note><note n="0060013" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30489"/>【佛拓】，或【史】</note><app n="0060013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">或</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30489"/></rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0060a24" type="honorific"/>伊我君公。秉心淵默。深覩正真。妙達通塞。
<lb ed="I" n="0060a25" type="honorific"/>淹迴聖迹。寢息神光。裁辯<app type="star" corresp="#0060009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">權</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30488"/></rdg></app>實。離<note n="0060014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30490"/>＝柝【史】</note><note n="0060014" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30490"/>【佛拓】，柝【史】</note><app n="0060014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">柝</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30490"/></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0060007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">舊</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30493"/></rdg></app><note n="0060015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30494"/>＝章【史】</note><note n="0060015" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30494"/>【佛拓】，章【史】</note><app n="0060015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">章</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30494"/></rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0060a26" type="honorific"/>十塵外遣。五陰內忘。蒸斯沈溺。作彼舟<note n="0060016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">舤＝航【史】</note><note n="0060016" resp="ihp" type="mod">舤【佛拓】，航【史】</note><app n="0060016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">航</lem><rdg wit="【原】">舤</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0060a27" type="honorific"/>出宿一<note n="0060017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB02391"/>＝廛【史】</note><note n="0060017" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB02391"/>【佛拓】，廛【史】</note><app n="0060017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">廛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB02391"/></rdg></app>。遄臨百里。秋蝗遠飛。春翬近止。
<lb ed="I" n="0060a28" type="honorific"/>清淨未儔。蕳率誰擬。方覲彌陀。遽淪濛汜。
<lb ed="I" n="0060a29" type="honorific"/>咨余小子。末命將淪。構茲寶塔。綴此遺塵。
<lb ed="I" n="0060a30" type="honorific"/>崇功去劫。樹善來因。舟壑雖改。永播天人。</p>
